            <p class="size26 str500 colorPrimary">Barangay Valdefuente</p>
            <p class="size12 str400 textJustify">Valdefuente, a barangay in Cabanatuan City, Nueva Ecija, Philippines, is known for its connection to historical events and its location along the General Luna Bridge and River. It is situated beside Barangay Mayapyap Sur and is along the Pan-Philippine Highway, also known as the Maharlika Highway. The area has been historically vulnerable to natural disasters like earthquakes and typhoons. </p>
