            <p class="size12">&bull; The area is near the former Cabanatuan Prison Camp, where American soldiers were held during World War II.</p>
            <p class="size12">&bull; The Raid at Cabanatuan, a successful rescue mission by American forces, took place near Valdefuente. </p>
